qMetaDef.description: For analyzing Professional, Analyzer, and Analyzer Capacity usage across multiple Qlik environments - both Qlik Sense and QlikView.
qMetaDef.title: Unified Licensing History

qMsg.qv: No Analyzer Capacity Minutes Used for current selections.

customErrorMessage.calcCond: No Analyzer Capacity Minutes Used for current selections.

qProperty.title: Unified License Consumption by App
qProperty.subtitle: QlikView apps are assigned to a generic "QlikView" stream.

qStringExpression.qExpr:
='Analyzer Capacity Minutes usage should be viewed by month because minutes renew the first day of each calendar month.'
& IF(license_type_enabled<>'Token-based' 
	AND [License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]>0
    AND Not Sum([Analyzer Capacity Used (Minutes)])>0,
    '* Analyzer Capacity Minutes usage is captured historically in the logs starting in June 2019 Sense.' &
    ' Earlier versions of Sense will report Analyzer Capacity Minutes = 0 in this chart even though minutes were used historically.'
    ,'')

qMsg.qv: No Analyzer Capacity Minutes Used for current selections.

customErrorMessage.calcCond: No Analyzer Capacity Minutes Used for current selections.

qStringExpression.qExpr:
='So far this month (' & MonthName(today(1)) & '), ' 
& Num(Sum({<month_to_date={1},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [Analyzer Capacity Used (Minutes)]),'#,##0')
& ' Analyzer Capacity minutes were used by ' 
& Num(count({<month_to_date={1},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"},[Analyzer Capacity Used (Minutes)]={">0"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') 
& ' users. Averages: ' 
& Num(Avg(Aggr(Sum({<month_to_date={1},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [Analyzer Capacity Used (Minutes)]),UserId)),'#,##0')
& ' minutes per user, '
& Num(Avg(Aggr(Sum({<month_to_date={1},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [Analyzer Capacity Used (Minutes)]),[Access Date])),'#,##0')
& ' minutes per day.'

=If(Count({<[Access Type]={"*"}>} IF(Len(UserId)<=1, UserId))>0,
	'Note: Blank User Id might indicate user identification error in QlikView Server. Please refer to the QlikView Server Events log or the QV Governance Dashboard for more information.'
    ,'')

qDef.qDef:
='Sense: ' & EngineVer 
& ' (' & Concat({<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Sense"}>} Distinct Hostname,',') & ') '
& If(qlikview_license_logs_present=1,'; Qlikview: ' & qlikview_maxstring_exe_version
	& ' (' & Concat({<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"}>} Distinct Hostname,',') & ') '
    )

='Current Month >> Professional Users: ' & Num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"*"},[Access Type]={"Professional"},month_to_date={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' Total ('
        & num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Professional"},month_to_date={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' QlikView)'
& Chr(10) & 'Analyzer Users: ' & Num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"*"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer"},month_to_date={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' Total ('
        & num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer"},month_to_date={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' QlikView)'
& Chr(10) & 'Analyzer Capacity Users: ' & Num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"*"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"},month_to_date={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' Total ('
        & num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"},month_to_date={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' QlikView)'

='Last Month (' & MonthName(AddMonths(Today(1),-1)) & ') >> Professional Users: ' & Num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"*"},[Access Type]={"Professional"},last_month={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' Total ('
        & num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Professional"},last_month={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' QlikView)'
& Chr(10) & 'Analyzer Users: ' & Num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"*"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer"},last_month={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' Total ('
        & num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer"},last_month={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' QlikView)'
& Chr(10) & 'Analyzer Capacity Users: ' & Num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"*"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"},last_month={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' Total ('
        & num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"},last_month={'1'},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0') & ' QlikView)'

IF((license_type_enabled)='Token-based','Not Licensed',
    Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]),'#,##0') & ' licensed, '
    & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]),'#,##0') & ' used, '
    & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)])
    		- Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [License Unavailable Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)])
            - Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)])
            ,'#,##0') & ' available'
    )

IF((license_type_enabled)='Token-based','Not Licensed',
    'licensed = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Access"}>}[License Total Tokens]),'#,##0') 
    & ', unallocated = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Access"}>}[License Total Tokens]-[License Allocated Tokens]),'#,##0')
    & ', allocated = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Access"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]),'#,##0')
    & ', used = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Access"}>}[License Used Tokens]),'#,##0')
    & ', allocated but unused = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Access"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]-[License Used Tokens]),'#,##0')
    )

IF((license_type_enabled)='Token-based','Not Licensed',
    'licensed = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Total Tokens]),'#,##0') 
    & ', unallocated = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Total Tokens]-[License Allocated Tokens]),'#,##0')
    & ', allocated = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]),'#,##0')
    & ', used = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Used Tokens]),'#,##0')
    & ', allocated but unused = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]-[License Used Tokens]),'#,##0')
    )

qProperty.title: Unified License Consumption by Month
qProperty.subtitle: Count of Users. Note: The same user can show up in both QlikView and Qlik Sense, using the same license assignment.
qProperty.footnote: *Analyzer Capacity minutes renew each calendar month.
